+# Decisions
+
+This directory captures architectural and procedural decisions arising from ACP
+Pilots and ACP revision proposals.
+
+## Purpose
+
+- Record the rationale behind ACP changes
+- Link findings from `FINDINGS/` to concrete decisions
+- Provide a changelog-adjacent view of why the protocol evolved
+
+## Format
+
+Each decision follows a lightweight ADR (Architecture Decision Record) format:
+
+- **Title:** What was decided
+- **Context:** What triggered the decision (findings, pilot, external requirement)
+- **Decision:** The chosen approach
+- **Consequences:** What becomes easier or harder
+- **Status:** `Proposed` / `Accepted` / `Superseded` / `Deprecated`
+
+## Register
+
+| # | Date | Title | Status | Related Findings |
+|---|---|---|---|---|
+| — | — | — | — | — |
